          "reviewBody": "The school blends modern learning with strong fundamentals by using smart boards along with traditional boards, ensuring clear understanding for every child. Beyond academics, students are encouraged to explore their talents through karate, dance practice, and sports like football and cricket. What truly touched me is how even parents are involved through friendly cricket matches, creating a strong school–parent bond.\nThe weekly assemblies are thoughtfully designed, giving students from all sections the opportunity to perform on stage and represent meaningful themes. This regular exposure builds confidence, communication skills, and courage in children. With excellent facilities, a safe environment, dedicated teachers, and a focus on overall personality development, Rameesh School is not just a school—it feels like a nurturing second home for our children.",
